VShUrY 'aShTh 'aBUrM L'a YLDH LV VLH ShPhChH MTShUrYTh VShMH HGUr.
VTh'aMUr ShUrY 'aL-'aBUrM HNH-N'a 'yTShUrNY YHVH MLDTh B'a-N'a 'aL-ShPhChThY 'aVLY 'aBNH MMNH VYShM'y 'aBUrM LQVL ShUrY.
VThQCh ShUrY 'aShTh-'aBUrM 'aTh-HGUr HMTShUrYTh ShPhChThH MQTSh 'yShUr ShNYM LShBTh 'aBUrM B'aUrTSh KN'yN VThThN 'aThH L'aBUrM 'aYShH LV L'aShH.
VYB'a 'aL-HGUr VThHUr VThUr'a KY HUrThH VThQL GBUrThH B'yYNYH.
VTh'aMUr ShUrY 'aL-'aBUrM ChMSY 'yLYK 'aNKY NThThY ShPhChThY BChYQK VThUr'a KY HUrThH V'aQL B'yYNYH YShPhT YHVH BYNY VBYNYK.
VY'aMUr 'aBUrM 'aL-ShUrY HNH ShPhChThK BYDK 'yShY-LH HTVB B'yYNYK VTh'yNH ShUrY VThBUrCh MPhNYH.
VYMTSh'aH ML'aK YHVH 'yL-'yYN HMYM BMDBUr 'yL-H'yYN BDUrK ShVUr.
VY'aMUr HGUr ShPhChTh ShUrY 'aY-MZH B'aTh V'aNH ThLKY VTh'aMUr MPhNY ShUrY GBUrThY 'aNKY BUrChTh.
VY'aMUr LH ML'aK YHVH ShVBY 'aL-GBUrThK VHTh'yNY ThChTh YDYH.
VY'aMUr LH ML'aK YHVH HUrBH 'aUrBH 'aTh-ZUr'yK VL'a YSPhUr MUrB.
VY'aMUr LH ML'aK YHVH HNK HUrH VYLDTh BN VQUr'aTh ShMV YShM'y'aL KY-ShM'y YHVH 'aL-'yNYK.
VHV'a YHYH PhUr'a 'aDM YDV BKL VYD KL BV V'yL-PhNY KL-'aChYV YShKN.
VThQUr'a ShM-YHVH HDBUr 'aLYH 'aThH 'aL Ur'aY KY 'aMUrH HGM HLM Ur'aYThY 'aChUrY Ur'aY.
'yL-KN QUr'a LB'aUr B'aUr LChY Ur'aY HNH BYN-QDSh VBYN BUrD.
VThLD HGUr L'aBUrM BN VYQUr'a 'aBUrM ShM-BNV 'aShUr-YLDH HGUr YShM'y'aL.
V'aBUrM BN-ShMNYM ShNH VShSh ShNYM BLDTh-HGUr 'aTh-YShM'y'aL L'aBUrM.
